      <title>I Hugged a Blåhaj Too Tight and Turned Into a Sharkgirl</title>
      <author> Querelle </author>
      <link>https://www.scribblehub.com/series/2120427/i-hugged-a-blhaj-too-tight-and-turned-into-a-sharkgirl/</link>
